docs.lead_paragraph: HEMPSTEAD, L.I., April 23. -- The first of the bicentenary celebration of the Church of St. George of Hempstead was held here to-day. The celebration was one of the most important events in the history of the Long Island Episcopal diocese.

headline.main: ST. GEORGE'S BICENTENARY.; Elaborate Celebration of the Birthday of Old Hempstead Church.
